src/lib/components/YasqeDcc.react.js.description:
YasqeDcc is a component which provides SPARQL syntax highlighting.
It takes a property, `query` which should be a SPARQl qeury, and
displays it.

id.description: The ID used to identify this component in Dash callbacks

value.description: A query that will be displayed in the editor.

setProps.description:
Dash-assigned callback that should be called whenever any of the
properties change

className.description: Often used with CSS to style elements with common properties.
